Package etm.core.monitor.event

Event subsystem.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AggregationListener A listener that informs about aggration detail changes.
AggregationStateListener A listener that informs about aggregated state changes.
CollectionListener A listener for receiving notifications on newly collected performance results.
CollectionStatusListener A listener that informs collection status changes.
EtmMonitorListener Base interface for our listeners.
EventDispatcher The event dispatcher will be used to dispatch events to registered listeners.
 

Class Summary
AggregationStateLoadedEvent Indicates that the aggregation state was loaded.
CollectEvent An event that indicates that a new result was collected.
CollectionDisabledEvent Indicates that collection of monitoring details was disabled
CollectionEnabledEvent Informs that collection of monitoring details was enabled.
DefaultEventDispatcher Default event dispatcher implementation.
EtmMonitorEvent Base class for our events.
MonitorResetEvent An event that informs that all aggregated details where deleted.
PreMonitorResetEvent An event that informs that all aggregated details are about to be deleted.
PreRootResetEvent An event that informs that a aggregation root will be resetted.
RootCreateEvent A event that indicates that a new top level aggregation result was created.
RootResetEvent An event that informs that a aggregation root was resetted.
